{"tid":2437531,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"北京宣佈將在外國設立「國產疫苗地區接種點」","createTime":"2021-03-08T02:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-08T03:53:38.000Z","uid":39464,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"8c2296a6979974bb067e4593a88a2744a5768195","tid":2437531,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:34:17.000Z","msg":"中國國務委員兼外交部長王毅宣佈將推出「春苗行動」，為身在海外的中國公民注射新冠病毒疫苗，並「在具備條件的國家設立國產疫苗地區接種點」。<br />\n<br />\n王毅昨日（3月7日）在中國全國人大會議記者會上表示，「春苗行動」的目的是「積極協助和爭取為海外同胞接種國產或外國疫苗」。<br />\n<br />\n他稱，當前已經有50多個國家正陸續將中國公民納入本國疫苗接種計劃，還有不少中國公民正在當地依法接種中國疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n「下一步我們還準備在具備條件的國家設立國產疫苗地區接種點，為周邊國家有需要的同胞提供服務。」<br />\n<br />\n目前澳洲本身的全國疫苗接種計劃正在進行，SBS中文正就中國的「春苗行動」向澳洲衛生部查詢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/china-says-it-s-ready-to-provide-vaccines-to-overseas-chinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fchinese%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Fchina-says-it-s-ready-to-provide-vaccines-to-overseas-chinese&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058rXqul57XbQM8lVYa5HUNM4%3D&h=9c7ee26d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/china-says-it-s-ready-to-provide-vaccines-to-overseas-chinese</a>"},{"pid":"d07f4fa5222e36168dfe2982980e5dbc31e4296d","tid":2437531,"uid":224533,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:36:33.000Z","msg":"以作推廣安樂死"},{"pid":"0002ff363eb5a7e93d24e8a5abd992cfc28084f3","tid":2437531,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:36:36.000Z","msg":"疫苗外交 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788d0c4b315ce77905985cf1775fac874484935c","tid":2437531,"uid":66049,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:36:59.000Z","msg":"見一個舉報一個犯叛國罪"},{"pid":"397a12067f9e6eb6bcd3a1cc61b0e022ffc2e57d","tid":2437531,"uid":163801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-08T02:38:13.000Z","msg":"佢哋憑咩去人哋國家幫人打針??"},{"pid":"f47